title: Trio Töykeät
text:
Trio Töykeät (founded in 1988) was a Finnish jazz trio. Their music ranges from humorous ragtimes to sentimental waltzes. Their playing style is often rhythmic, energetic and virtuosic. The group disbanded in 2008. [1]


== Members ==
Iiro Rantala – piano
Rami Eskelinen – drums
Eerik Siikasaari – double bass


== Releases ==
Päivää (1990)
G'day (1993) (international re-release of Päivää)
Jazzlantis (1995)
Rappiolla (1997)
Sisu (1997)
Kudos (2000)
Music! (2002)
High Standards (2003)
Wake (2005)
One Night in Tampere (2007)
